 class=\"c-label\">Product<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"c-title\">NMS Key Features<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"c-page\">PAGE&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>11<\u002Fb><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 03 — Section 01 ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"03\" class=\"section-slide\" data-accent=\"blue-strong\">\n    <div class=\"edge-strip\" data-no-auto=\"\"><div class=\"seg orange\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"seg yellow\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"seg green\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"seg blue\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"left\">\n        <div class=\"section-num\"><span class=\"slash\">/<\u002Fspan>01<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"section-label\">Company Introduction<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>About<br>WhaTap Labs<\u002Fh2>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"right\">\n        <div class=\"topics\">\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">01 — 01<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Who we are &amp; company profile<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">01 — 02<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Certifications &amp; analyst recognition<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">01 — 03<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Full-stack observability platform<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">01 — 04<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Product architecture &amp; data flow<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 04 — About WhaTap Labs ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"04\" class=\"content\" data-foot=\"ABOUT WHATAP LABS\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"head-block\">\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\">About WhaTap Labs<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2 class=\"slide-title\">A decade of building Korea's <span class=\"accent\">AI-Native Observability Platform.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fh2>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"about-grid\">\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"about-lede\">\n            Founded in July 2015, WhaTap Labs is now in its <strong>twelfth year<\u002Fstrong> as a specialist in AI-based IT monitoring. As <strong>Korea's first SaaS-based monitoring service<\u002Fstrong>, WhaTap has grown into a full-stack <strong>AI-Native Observability platform<\u002Fstrong> spanning GPU, applications, servers, databases, Kubernetes and more.\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"about-stats\">\n            <div class=\"about-stat\"><div class=\"num\">2015<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"lbl\">Founded<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"about-stat\"><div class=\"num\">1,200+<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"lbl\">Customers<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"about-stat\"><div class=\"num\">93<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"lbl\">Employees<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"info-grid\">\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">Established<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">July 2015<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">CEO<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">Dongin Lee<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">Capital<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">KRW 469,867,400<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">Headcount<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">93 (as of Sep 2025)<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">Contact<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">Tel. 02-565-1803 · Fax. 0504-848-1803<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">Website<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">www.whatap.io<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"info-row\"><div class=\"k\">Headquarters<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"v\">17 Gasan digital 1-ro 77-gil, 13F #1301, Geumcheon-gu, Seoul (06614)<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 05 — Certifications & Gartner ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"05\" class=\"content\" data-foot=\"CERTIFICATIONS\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"head-block\">\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\">Trust &amp; Recognition<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2 class=\"slide-title\">Certified for security, validated by the market.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">WhaTap secures domestic and international certifications across cloud and information security, and is recognized in the Gartner® 2025 Market Guide.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"cert-grid\">\n        <div class=\"cert-card c1\">\n          <div class=\"cc-tag\">Information Security<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>ISO 27001 · 27017<br>27018 · 27701<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>International standards for information security, cloud security and privacy management.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"cert-card c2\">\n          <div class=\"cc-tag\">Cloud Service<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>KCSP · CSAP<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Korea Cloud Service Provider and Cloud Security Assurance Program certifications for public-sector cloud.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"cert-card c3\">\n          <div class=\"cc-tag\">Quality<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>GS Certification<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Good Software Grade 1 — the highest software-quality grade in Korea.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"cert-card c4\">\n          <div class=\"cc-tag\">Analyst<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>Gartner® 2025<br>Market Guide<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Listed in the Market Guide for Infrastructure Monitoring Tools.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"gartner-band\">\n        <div class=\"gb-mark\">Gartner® 2025<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"gb-text\">Named a <b>Representative Vendor<\u002Fb> in the 2025 Market Guide for Infrastructure Monitoring Tools — the <b>only Korean vendor<\u002Fb> recognized — and selected as a \"2025 Representative Company.\"<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 06 — Vision statement ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"06\" class=\"content statement-slide\" data-foot=\"WHY OBSERVABILITY\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"bar-accent\"><span class=\"seg s1\"><\u002Fspan><span class=\"seg s2\"><\u002Fspan><span class=\"seg s3\"><\u002Fspan><span class=\"seg s4\"><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"st-head\">Unified monitoring and observability for the <span class=\"accent\">cloud and virtualization<\u002Fspan> era.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"st-sub\">As infrastructure shifts from on-premise equipment to cloud and virtualized environments, monitoring has to move from being equipment-centric to service- and process-centric — with full-stack visibility on a single platform.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"st-art\">\n        <img src=\"e62ab98d-b1db-4ae3-9e03-455d36e1a2b6\" alt=\"WhaTap full-stack observability illustration\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 07 — Full-stack lineup ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"07\" class=\"content\" data-foot=\"PRODUCT LINEUP\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"head-block\">\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\">One Integrated SaaS Platform<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2 class=\"slide-title\">Full-stack monitoring across every layer of your stack.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">From network and GPU to applications, databases, containers and logs — all observed on one unified WhaTap platform.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"lineup-grid\">\n        <div class=\"lineup-card feature\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-blue)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Network Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\"><b>Vendors:<\u002Fb> Cisco, Juniper, Huawei, HP, ArubaOS, Dell, F5, Fortinet, Checkpoint, VMware, Extreme, Arista, Palo Alto, Citrix, SonicWall, EMC, Netgear &amp; more<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-orange)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Real User · URL Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\"><b>Browsers:<\u002Fb> Chrome, Edge, Safari, Firefox, Opera, Chrome Android, Safari iOS, Samsung Internet<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-green)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Server Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\"><b>OS:<\u002Fb> Windows, Linux<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-yellow)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Application Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\"><b>Languages:<\u002Fb> Java, Node.js, Python, PHP, .NET, Go<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-blue)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Kubernetes Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\"><b>Platforms:<\u002Fb> Amazon EKS, AKS, GKE, OKE, Naver Cloud Kubernetes (NKS), RedHat OpenShift, Rancher, Kakao i Cloud &amp; more<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-orange)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Database Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\"><b>DBs:<\u002Fb> Oracle, Tibero, MySQL, MariaDB, CUBRID, Altibase, Redis, EDB PostgreSQL, MongoDB · Oracle DMA<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-green)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">Log Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\">Collection, parsing, search and alerting for application and system logs.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-yellow)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">GPU Monitoring<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\">Real-time visibility for GPU resources running AI workloads.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"lineup-card\" style=\"--lc:var(--bar-blue)\">\n          <div class=\"lc-name\">OpenMetrics<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"lc-support\">Prometheus-compatible metric collection for custom and third-party sources.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 08 — Architecture ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"08\" class=\"content\" data-foot=\"PRODUCT ARCHITECTURE\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"head-block\">\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\">Product Architecture · Deployment<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2 class=\"slide-title\">A distributed collection architecture, ready for any scale.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">Agents feed a distributed pipeline of Gate, Yard and Front tiers — available as SaaS or as a separately installed (on-premise) deployment for stricter security needs.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"nflow\">\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-orange)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Collect<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>Agent<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Lightweight agents collect metrics from servers, network devices and VMs across the environment.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>Server / VM<\u002Fspan><span>Network<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-arrow\" data-arrow=\"\"><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-yellow)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Gateway<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>Proxy · Gate<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>The collection gateway receives, processes and routes incoming data from every agent.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>Collection<\u002Fspan><span>Routing<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-arrow\" data-arrow=\"\"><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-green)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Store<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>Yard<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Distributed data store that scales horizontally for high-volume time-series data.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>Data store<\u002Fspan><span>Scale-out<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-arrow\" data-arrow=\"\"><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-blue)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Serve<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>Front<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Web UI and APIs that present dashboards, monitoring and analytics to operators.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>Dashboards<\u002Fspan><span>API<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 09 — Data collection & transfer ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"09\" class=\"content\" data-foot=\"DATA COLLECTION &amp; TRANSFER\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"head-block\">\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\">Product Architecture · Data Flow<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2 class=\"slide-title\">Collected data is encrypted end to end, agent to server.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">WhaTap agents gather execution and statistical data, then transmit it to the WhaTap server over AES- and SSL-encrypted channels.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"nflow\">\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-orange)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Source<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>WhaTap Agent<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Collects SQL execution details, transaction and metric data directly from the workload.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>SQL stats<\u002Fspan><span>HTTP stats<\u002Fspan><span>Metrics<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-arrow\" data-arrow=\"\"><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-green)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Secure Transfer<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>AES · SSL Encryption<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Data is encrypted in transit so sensitive operational information is protected on the wire.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>AES<\u002Fspan><span>SSL/TLS<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-arrow\" data-arrow=\"\"><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"nflow-step\" style=\"--fs:var(--bar-blue)\">\n          <div class=\"ns-label\">Destination<\u002Fdiv>\n          <h3>WhaTap Server<\u002Fh3>\n          <p>Receives, stores and analyzes the data, then serves it back through dashboards and alerts.<\u002Fp>\n          <div class=\"ns-chips\"><span>Store<\u002Fspan><span>Analyze<\u002Fspan><span>Visualize<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 10 — Log collection & analysis ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"10\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"LOG COLLECTION &amp; ANALYSIS\" data-accent=\"green\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span>Product Architecture · Logs<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Logs collected, parsed and indexed for everyone.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">A single log pipeline serves both developers and infrastructure managers — from raw collection through parsing, indexing and metrics.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Collect → Parse → Index / Metrics<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Logs from PHP, Go, .NET, Java, Python, Node.js, servers, cloud, containers and Kubernetes flow into one pipeline.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>For developers<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Live Tail, Search, Analysis and Linking to trace issues quickly down to the request.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>For infrastructure managers<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Dashboards, Exception tracking, Reports and Alerts for day-to-day operations.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right\">\n        <img src=\"e67b6790-4562-4fcf-bd38-2b97b437b399\" alt=\"WhaTap log search\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 11 — Section 02 ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"11\" class=\"section-slide\" data-accent=\"orange\">\n    <div class=\"edge-strip\" data-no-auto=\"\"><div class=\"seg orange\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"seg yellow\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"seg green\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"seg blue\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"left\">\n        <div class=\"section-num\"><span class=\"slash\">/<\u002Fspan>02<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"section-label\">Network Management System<\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>NMS<br>Key Features<\u002Fh2>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"right\">\n        <div class=\"topics\">\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">02 — 01<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Topology &amp; dashboards<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">02 — 02<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Device, interface &amp; port monitoring<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">02 — 03<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Discovery, MIB &amp; API integration<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"topic\"><div class=\"topic-num\">02 — 04<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"topic-title\">Events, alerts &amp; log management<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 12 — Topology ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"12\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · TOPOLOGY\" data-accent=\"orange\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">01<\u002Fspan><span>Topology — Configuration Map<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>See the whole network, exactly as it is wired.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Auto-discovered, fully editable topology with physical and logical views and real-time status — no manual diagramming required.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Auto discovery &amp; mapping<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Auto Discovery finds network devices and builds the topology and connection relationships automatically.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Drag &amp; drop editing<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Rearrange devices and layouts by drag &amp; drop, with grouping and zone (area) settings.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Physical &amp; logical views<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Switch between physical and logical (isometric) views, plus separate monitoring and edit modes.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Status visualization<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Fault states are reflected in real time through color and icon cues across the map.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right stack\">\n        <span class=\"cap\">Physical view<\u002Fspan>\n        <img src=\"bd68c7b1-c3c9-4139-9253-6d78c4b79128\" alt=\"NMS physical topology\">\n        <span class=\"cap\">Logical (isometric) view<\u002Fspan>\n        <img src=\"3e12b4c2-2b1e-45cc-ba7c-40056da74004\" alt=\"NMS logical topology\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 13 — Dashboard ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"13\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · DASHBOARD\" data-accent=\"yellow\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">02<\u002Fspan><span>Dashboard — Network Overview<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Your whole network's health, on one screen.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">A configurable overview built from TOP-N rankings and status widgets, so operators can read the state of the network at a glance and drill in where needed.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Core widgets<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Device Count, Throughput ranking, status distribution, PPS ranking, last-24h Syslog, Trap event TOP 10 and Health Check.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Customizable per widget<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Tune the data and display options for each widget independently.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Per–Control Manager views<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>View dashboards scoped to each Control Manager instance.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right\">\n        <img src=\"0c29e26a-ba16-4a3d-9245-ff56b9b78f20\" alt=\"WhaTap integrated dashboard\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 14 — Fault-status monitoring ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"14\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"green\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">03<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — Status by Fault<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Spot faults the moment they happen.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Real-time, color-coded status monitoring with drill-down, so a developing problem is visible immediately and traceable to its source.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Per-device Up / Down status<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Device and fault states are visualized in real time across the monitored network.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Threshold-based detection<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Status changes based on configured thresholds make abnormal conditions stand out instantly.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Drill-down to detail<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Move from a status indicator straight into the detailed metrics behind it.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right\">\n        <img src=\"bd68c7b1-c3c9-4139-9253-6d78c4b79128\" alt=\"NMS fault-status monitoring\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 15 — Interface monitoring ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"15\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"blue\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">04<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — Interface<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Per-interface traffic, link state and trends.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Track traffic on every interface and follow link state changes with drill-down into the underlying detail.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Traffic by interface<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Peak and total Inbound / Outbound traffic measured per interface.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Link Up / Down with drill-down<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Color-coded link state, with drill-down from any interface into its detail view.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Threshold &amp; trend views<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Set thresholds per interface and review historical traffic trends.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Interface Traffic<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Inbound — Peak<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">▲ 23.35 Kbps<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Outbound — Peak<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">▼ 16.92 Kbps<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Total throughput<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">aggregated<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Link state<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">UP / DOWN<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Drill-down<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">per interface<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Peak / Total and Inbound / Outbound metrics are tracked for each interface, with color-coded link status.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 16 — Port monitoring ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"16\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"orange\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">05<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — Port<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Every switch port, accounted for.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Port-level visibility into traffic and status, so capacity and connectivity issues surface before they spread.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Status &amp; traffic per port<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Monitor connection status and traffic for each individual port.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Peak / average traffic<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Compare peak and average port traffic to understand utilization.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Thresholds &amp; alerts<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Set per-port thresholds and raise alerts when limits are crossed.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Port Status<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Active ports<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">connected<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Traffic — Peak<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">per port<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Traffic — Average<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">per port<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Utilization<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">monitored<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Threshold alerts<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">enabled<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Per-port connection status and Peak / average traffic with configurable thresholds and alerting.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 17 — Map view ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"17\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"yellow\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">06<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — Map View<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Monitor the network where it physically lives.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Place devices on a Site / Building / Floor hierarchy and watch status by physical location, so an outage maps straight to a place.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Site · Building · Floor hierarchy<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Organize devices across a multi-level physical structure that mirrors your facilities.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Status by location<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Device and fault states are shown directly on the map for each location.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Navigate top-down<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Drill from a site down to a specific building, floor and device.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Location Hierarchy<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Site<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">level 1<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Building<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">level 2<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Floor<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">level 3<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Device placement<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">on map<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Status overlay<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">real-time<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Devices are mapped onto a Site / Building / Floor structure with real-time status by physical location.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 18 — Device inventory ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"18\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"green\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">07<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — Device Inventory<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>One source of truth for every device.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Manage all NMS device information in one place — identity, addressing and SNMP polling configuration per device.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Device identity<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Manage Alias, Host, Hostname and, for SNMP agents, IP and Hostname details.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Per-device polling &amp; rules<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Configure Polling and Rules individually for each device.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>OID &amp; MIB Browser<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Look up OID values with the MIB Browser and attach them to devices.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>ICMP / TCP health check<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Run end-point Health Checks over ICMP / TCP for reachability and service status.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Device Record<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Alias / Host / Hostname<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">managed<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">SNMP IP<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">per device<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Polling &amp; Rules<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">configurable<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">OID lookup<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">MIB Browser<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Health check<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">ICMP / TCP<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Centralized device records with per-device SNMP polling, OID mapping and end-point health checks.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 19 — MIB browser / OID ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"19\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"blue\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">08<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — MIB Browser / OID<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Search, load and manage SNMP OIDs with ease.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Browse standard and private MIBs, search OID trees, and compose the exact objects you want to poll and visualize.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Load MIBs, search OIDs<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Load SNMP MIB modules and search the OID tree to find the objects you need.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Private MIB upload<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Upload private MIBs and manage their OID definitions for vendor-specific devices.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Per-device SNMP version<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Set the SNMP version per device and compose OIDs accordingly.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Visualize collected OIDs<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Turn collected OID values into charts and views for monitoring.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">MIB / OID Manager<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Standard MIB<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">load / search<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Private MIB<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">upload<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">OID tree<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">browse<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">SNMP version<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">v1 / v2c / v3<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Visualization<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">charts<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Load standard and private MIBs, search the OID tree, and visualize collected OID values per device.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 20 — API integration ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"20\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · INTEGRATION\" data-accent=\"orange\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">09<\u002Fspan><span>API Integration<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Open RESTful APIs to plug into your stack.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Query and manage NMS data through RESTful APIs, and connect cleanly to the operational tools you already run.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>RESTful API access<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Retrieve device, status and metric data programmatically over standard REST endpoints.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Integrate with ops tools<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Connect to ITSM, APM, CMDB and SIEM systems to fit existing workflows.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Automate &amp; extend<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Build custom automations and reporting on top of the open API surface.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right\">\n        <img src=\"69cac2ce-946d-4d19-a7dc-77db6754e6d1\" alt=\"NMS RESTful API (OpenAPI)\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 21 — Health check ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"21\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · MONITORING\" data-accent=\"yellow\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">10<\u002Fspan><span>Monitoring — Health Check<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Know whether the service actually answers.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Active ICMP / TCP checks confirm that end-points are reachable and responding — not just that a device is powered on.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>ICMP / TCP checks<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Probe end-points over ICMP and TCP to verify reachability and service response.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Per-target configuration<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Define which end-points to check and on what schedule.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Status into alerts<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Feed health-check results into the same events and alerting pipeline.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Health Check<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">ICMP<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">reachability<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">TCP<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">service port<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">End-points<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">per target<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Schedule<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">configurable<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Result<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">→ alerts<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Active ICMP / TCP probes verify that end-points respond, feeding status into the alerting pipeline.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 22 — Events & alerts ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"22\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · EVENTS &amp; ALERTS\" data-accent=\"green\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">11<\u002Fspan><span>Events &amp; Alerts<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Turn every signal into the right notification.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">SNMP Traps, Syslog and Health Check results all flow into one event engine — with flexible rules and multi-channel delivery.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Unified event sources<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>SNMP Trap, Syslog, Health Check and threshold events are collected together.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Flexible alert rules<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Define conditions and policies for which events should raise alerts.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Multi-channel delivery<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Send notifications by email, SMS and messenger to the right people.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Alert Channels<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">SNMP Trap<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">source<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Syslog<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">source<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Health Check<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">source<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Email · SMS<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">delivery<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">Messenger<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">delivery<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">One event engine across Trap, Syslog and Health Check, with rule-based routing to email, SMS and messenger.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 23 — Trap / Syslog ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"23\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · TRAP / SYSLOG\" data-accent=\"blue\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">12<\u002Fspan><span>Events — Trap / Syslog<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Classify and act on Traps and Syslog by severity.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">SNMP Trap and Syslog messages are collected, classified by severity and made searchable — and can be forwarded to a SIEM.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Real-time collection<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Traps and Syslog from devices are received and displayed in real time.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Severity classification<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Messages are organized by Severity Level (0–7) for fast triage.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>SIEM forwarding<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Forward events to SIEM and other systems for correlation and retention.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right stack\">\n        <span class=\"cap\">SNMP Traps<\u002Fspan>\n        <img src=\"8e9fa9ce-831f-46dc-bc04-590c050329e6\" alt=\"NMS SNMP Traps\">\n        <span class=\"cap\">Syslog<\u002Fspan>\n        <img src=\"f9318b6f-c489-4784-90dc-58ca0dabdfe5\" alt=\"NMS Syslog\">\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 24 — Log management ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"24\" class=\"content feature-slide\" data-foot=\"NMS · LOG MANAGEMENT\" data-accent=\"orange\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"feat-left\">\n        <div class=\"feat-eyebrow\"><span class=\"num\">13<\u002Fspan><span>Log Management<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Search, filter and export collected logs.<\u002Fh2>\n        <div class=\"feat-summary\">Find what matters across collected logs with rich filtering, then export raw or structured data for reporting and audit.<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"bullets\">\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Filter by key fields<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Search and filter by Host IP, OID and Category to narrow down quickly.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>CSV &amp; RAW export<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>Export results as CSV or RAW data for downstream analysis and reporting.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"bullet\"><div class=\"marker\"><\u002Fdiv><div>\n            <h3>Searchable fields<\u002Fh3>\n            <p>agenttime, host, oid, oname and severity are all available as query fields.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"feat-right spec-panel\">\n        <div class=\"sp-head\"><span class=\"sp-title\">Searchable Fields<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-bars\"><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><i><\u002Fi><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-rows\">\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">agenttime<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">timestamp<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">host<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">device<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">oid<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">object id<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">oname<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">object name<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"sp-row\"><span class=\"sp-k\">severity<\u002Fspan><span class=\"sp-v\">level<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"sp-foot\">Filter by Host IP, OID and Category, then export matching logs as CSV or RAW data.<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n  <!-- ============ SLIDE 25 — Closing / contact ============ -->\n  <section data-screen-label=\"25\" class=\"content closing-slide\" data-foot=\"THANK YOU\">\n    <div class=\"slide-pad\">\n      <div class=\"head-block\">\n        <div class=\"bar-accent\"><span class=\"seg s1\"><\u002Fspan><span class=\"seg s2\"><\u002Fspan><span class=\"seg s3\"><\u002Fspan><span class=\"seg s4\"><\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <h2>Let's monitor your network, <span class=\"accent\">end to end.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fh2>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"contact-grid\">\n        <div class=\"contact-item\"><div class=\"ci-k\">Company<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"ci-v\">WhaTap Labs Inc.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"contact-item\"><div class=\"ci-k\">Established<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"ci-v\">July 1, 2015<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"contact-item\"><div class=\"ci-k\">Website<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"ci-v\"><a href=\"https://www.whatap.io\">www.whatap.io<\u002Fa><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"contact-item\"><div class=\"ci-k\">Phone<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"ci-v\">02-565-1803<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"contact-item\"><div class=\"ci-k\">Sales · Support<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"ci-v\"><a href=\"mailto:sales@whatap.io\">sales@whatap.io<\u002Fa> · <a href=\"mailto:support@whatap.io\">support@whatap.io<\u002Fa><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <div class=\"contact-item\"><div class=\"ci-k\">Address<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"ci-v\">17 Gasan digital 1-ro 77-gil, 13F #1303, Seoul<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n<\u002Fdeck-stage>\n\n<!-- Bundler splash / no-JS fallback -->\n\n\n<script>\n/* Inject shared slide chrome (edge strip, corner logo